&lt;/ul>
&lt;h4>Feature Card&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="feature-card">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#feature-card" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h4>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>hextra-feature-card&lt;/code> - The feature card link element&lt;/li>
